{
  "video_id": "gbDraZi7F_4",
  "title": "Courage is contagious | Damon Davis",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13232.0,
      "end_time": 14517.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15438.0,
      "end_time": 16892.0,
      "text": "Right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16916.0,
      "end_time": 18437.0,
      "text": "on this stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18461.0,
      "end_time": 19679.0,
      "text": "I feel fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20919.0,
      "end_time": 22622.0,
      "text": "In my life, I ain&#39;t met many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22646.0,
      "end_time": 24876.0,
      "text": "that will readily admit when they are afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25418.0,
      "end_time": 27461.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s because deep down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27485.0,
      "end_time": 29192.0,
      "text": "they know how easy it spreads."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30288.0,
      "end_time": 31843.0,
      "text": "See, fear is like a disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32732.0,
      "end_time": 35190.0,
      "text": "When it moves, it moves like wildfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35732.0,
      "end_time": 37310.0,
      "text": "But what happens when,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37334.0,
      "end_time": 39840.0,
      "text": "even in the face of that fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39108.0,
      "end_time": 40595.0,
      "text": "you do what you&#39;ve got to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41114.0,
      "end_time": 42443.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s called courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43174.0,
      "end_time": 44857.0,
      "text": "And just like fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44881.0,
      "end_time": 46263.0,
      "text": "courage is contagious."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47690.0,
      "end_time": 49937.0,
      "text": "See, I&#39;m from East St. Louis, Illinois."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49963.0,
      "end_time": 51122.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a small city"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51147.0,
      "end_time": 53961.0,
      "text": "across the Mississippi River from St. Louis, Missouri."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53985.0,
      "end_time": 58580.0,
      "text": "I have lived in and around St. Louis my entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60263.0,
      "end_time": 61567.0,
      "text": "When Michael Brown, Jr.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61591.0,
      "end_time": 62843.0,
      "text": "an ordinary teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62867.0,
      "end_time": 67417.0,
      "text": "was gunned down by police in 2014 in Ferguson, Missouri --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67441.0,
      "end_time": 70600.0,
      "text": "another suburb, but north of St. Louis --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70624.0,
      "end_time": 72157.0,
      "text": "I remember thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72181.0,
      "end_time": 73940.0,
      "text": "he ain&#39;t the first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73964.0,
      "end_time": 77828.0,
      "text": "and he won&#39;t be the last young kid to lose his life to law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78308.0,
      "end_time": 79969.0,
      "text": "But see, his death was different."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80885.0,
      "end_time": 82208.0,
      "text": "When Mike was killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82232.0,
      "end_time": 85696.0,
      "text": "I remember the powers that be trying to use fear as a weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87000.0,
      "end_time": 90528.0,
      "text": "The police response to a community in mourning was to use force"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90552.0,
      "end_time": 91775.0,
      "text": "to impose fear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92564.0,
      "end_time": 94181.0,
      "text": "fear of militarized police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94733.0,
      "end_time": 95962.0,
      "text": "imprisonment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95986.0,
      "end_time": 97155.0,
      "text": "fines."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97179.0,
      "end_time": 99699.0,
      "text": "The media even tried to make us afraid of each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99723.0,
      "end_time": 101275.0,
      "text": "by the way they spun the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101299.0,
      "end_time": 103658.0,
      "text": "And all of these things have worked in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103682.0,
      "end_time": 106296.0,
      "text": "But like I said, this time it was different."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107484.0,
      "end_time": 110857.0,
      "text": "Michael Brown&#39;s death and the subsequent treatment of the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110882.0,
      "end_time": 114619.0,
      "text": "led to a string of protests in and around Ferguson and St. Louis."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115380.0,
      "end_time": 119145.0,
      "text": "When I got out to those protests about the fourth or fifth day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 119169.0,
      "end_time": 120572.0,
      "text": "it was not out of courage;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121187.0,
      "end_time": 122499.0,
      "text": "it was out of guilt."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123315.0,
      "end_time": 124588.0,
      "text": "See, I&#39;m black."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125430.0,
      "end_time": 126788.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if y&#39;all noticed that."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126812.0,
      "end_time": 127837.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 127861.0,
      "end_time": 133338.0,
      "text": "But I couldn&#39;t sit in St. Louis, minutes away from Ferguson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133362.0,
      "end_time": 134831.0,
      "text": "and not go see."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134855.0,
      "end_time": 137297.0,
      "text": "So I got off my ass to go check it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137321.0,
      "end_time": 138761.0,
      "text": "When I got out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138785.0,
      "end_time": 141194.0,
      "text": "I found something surprising."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142470.0,
      "end_time": 144508.0,
      "text": "I found anger; there was a lot of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145327.0,
      "end_time": 147599.0,
      "text": "But what I found more of was love."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148565.0,
      "end_time": 150472.0,
      "text": "People with love for themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150497.0,
      "end_time": 152137.0,
      "text": "Love for their community."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152161.0,
      "end_time": 153850.0,
      "text": "And it was beautiful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153874.0,
      "end_time": 155463.0,
      "text": "until the police showed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 156495.0,
      "end_time": 160234.0,
      "text": "Then a new emotion was interjected into the conversation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160815.0,
      "end_time": 162180.0,
      "text": "fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162447.0,
      "end_time": 164132.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not going to lie;"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164156.0,
      "end_time": 166950.0,
      "text": "when I saw those armored vehicles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166974.0,
      "end_time": 168135.0,
      "text": "and all that gear"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168159.0,
      "end_time": 169525.0,
      "text": "and all those guns"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169549.0,
      "end_time": 171310.0,
      "text": "and all those police"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171334.0,
      "end_time": 172797.0,
      "text": "I was terrified --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172821.0,
      "end_time": 173996.0,
      "text": "personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175791.0,
      "end_time": 177545.0,
      "text": "And when I looked around that crowd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177569.0,
      "end_time": 180331.0,
      "text": "I saw a lot of people that had the same thing going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 180355.0,
      "end_time": 183548.0,
      "text": "But I also saw people with something else inside of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184500.0,
      "end_time": 185643.0,
      "text": "That was courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185667.0,
      "end_time": 187450.0,
      "text": "See, those people yelled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187690.0,
      "end_time": 188310.0,
      "text": "and they screamed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 188335.0,
      "end_time": 190887.0,
      "text": "and they were not about to back down from the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 190911.0,
      "end_time": 192559.0,
      "text": "They were past that point."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 192583.0,
      "end_time": 194834.0,
      "text": "And then I could feel something in me changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 194858.0,
      "end_time": 196496.0,
      "text": "so I yelled and I screamed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 197309.0,
      "end_time": 200797.0,
      "text": "and I noticed that everybody around me was doing the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 201647.0,
      "end_time": 203834.0,
      "text": "And there was nothing like that feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 204843.0,
      "end_time": 206929.0,
      "text": "So I decided I wanted to do something more."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 207425.0,
      "end_time": 210729.0,
      "text": "I went home, I thought: I&#39;m an artist. I make shit."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210753.0,
      "end_time": 214380.0,
      "text": "So I started making things specific to the protest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215912.0,
      "end_time": 218501.0,
      "text": "things that would be weapons in a spiritual war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 220257.0,
      "end_time": 222184.0,
      "text": "things that would give people voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223291.0,
      "end_time": 225940.0,
      "text": "and things that would fortify them for the road ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 226874.0,
      "end_time": 230287.0,
      "text": "I did a project where I took pictures of the hands of protesters"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 230311.0,
      "end_time": 234300.0,
      "text": "and put them up and down the boarded-up buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 234325.0,
      "end_time": 236000.0,
      "text": "and community shops."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 236690.0,
      "end_time": 240310.0,
      "text": "My goal was to raise awareness and to raise the morale."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240334.0,
      "end_time": 242735.0,
      "text": "And I think, for a minute at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242759.0,
      "end_time": 244500.0,
      "text": "it did just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 245770.0,
      "end_time": 249310.0,
      "text": "Then I thought, I want to uplift the stories of these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249334.0,
      "end_time": 251740.0,
      "text": "I was watching being courageous in the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 252258.0,
      "end_time": 255329.0,
      "text": "And myself and my friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 255950.0,
      "end_time": 257921.0,
      "text": "and filmmaker and partner Sabaah Folayan"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 257946.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260124.00000000003,
      "text": "did just that with our documentary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 260148.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261459.00000000003,
      "text": "\"Whose Streets?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 263316.0,
      "end_time": 265428.0,
      "text": "I kind of became a conduit"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 265452.0,
      "end_time": 268974.0,
      "text": "for all of this courage that was given to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 268998.0,
      "end_time": 272187.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s part of our job as artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 272836.0,
      "end_time": 276601.0,
      "text": "I think we should be conveyors of courage in the work that we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277154.0,
      "end_time": 281436.0,
      "text": "And I think that we are the wall between the normal folks"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 281460.0,
      "end_time": 284916.0,
      "text": "and the people that use their power to spread fear and hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 284940.0,
      "end_time": 286684.0,
      "text": "especially in times like these."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 288257.0,
      "end_time": 290580.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to ask you."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 290820.0,
      "end_time": 291860.0,
      "text": "Y&#39;all the movers and the shakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 292370.0,
      "end_time": 294424.0,
      "text": "you know, the thought leaders:"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 294448.0,
      "end_time": 296287.0,
      "text": "What are you gonna do"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 296312.0,
      "end_time": 298335.0,
      "text": "with the gifts that you&#39;ve been given"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 298359.0,
      "end_time": 300799.0,
      "text": "to break us from the fear the binds us every day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301580.0,
      "end_time": 303359.0,
      "text": "Because, see, I&#39;m afraid every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 304304.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t remember a time when I wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 307126.0,
      "end_time": 310566.0,
      "text": "But once I figured out that fear was not put in me to cripple me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 311393.0,
      "end_time": 313440.0,
      "text": "it was there to protect me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 313624.0,
      "end_time": 315952.0,
      "text": "and once I figured out how to use that fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 316644.0,
      "end_time": 318900.0,
      "text": "I found my power."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 318926.0,
      "end_time": 320122.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 320146.0,
      "end_time": 322748.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}